Name: assign_worker_to_task
Description: A binary variable indicating if a worker (w) is assigned to a task (tsk).

Name: assign_user_story_to_sprint
Description: A binary variable indicating if a user story (us) is included in a sprint (sp).

Name: assign_team_to_project
Description: A binary variable indicating if a team (t) is assigned to a project (p).

Name: assign_feature_to_release
Description: A binary variable indicating if a feature (f) is assigned to a release plan (rep).

Name: set_sprint_start_date
Description: The scheduled start date for a specific sprint.

Name: set_sprint_end_date
Description: The scheduled end date for a specific sprint.

Name: set_team_size
Description: The number of workers assigned to a specific team.

Name: allocate_worker_effort_to_task
Description: The percentage of a worker's capacity allocated to a specific task.

Name: set_feature_priority
Description: The priority level assigned to a feature, where a higher number is more important.

Name: select_sprint_for_backlog
Description: An integer representing the sprint ID a sprint backlog belongs to.

Name: set_user_story_story_points
Description: The estimated effort in story points for a user story.

Name: link_task_to_story
Description: An integer representing the user story ID a task is linked to.
